Note on scope: this MIT license covers the original code (Python simulator,
React/TypeScript teaching site, SVG diagrams) and the original commentary
written for this repository. The repository discusses a paper by D. Tasca
et al. (IEEE JSSC vol. 46 no. 12, pp. 2745-2758, Dec. 2011) but does not
include any of the paper's figures or text. All plots in `results/figures/`
are produced by the behavioral simulator under `sim/` and are clearly
labeled as such.
